WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.187
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.187 --> 00:00:03.497
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.497 --> 00:00:05.279
Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:05.649 --> 00:00:07.130
It's Diana and me.

00:00:07.870 --> 00:00:12.343
She's behind the camera and she's been reading to me all day.

00:00:12.343 --> 00:00:18.720
Our internet's been down because we had a big storm come through last night, but we got a lot of rain again and the Lord blessed us.

00:00:18.720 --> 00:00:22.080
But with no internet, no videos.

00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:27.889
So, we've been reading and she read a lot of things in the Old Testament to me from Nehemiah.

00:00:27.889 --> 00:00:31.053
And I told her, I said, 'You know, this is really interesting.

00:00:31.053 --> 00:00:35.817
Some of these prophetic men that walked the face of the earth went through so much.

00:00:35.817 --> 00:00:41.360
You know, I have nothing to complain about when I hear the stories of what they went through.

00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:43.309
I mean, my goodness!

00:00:43.309 --> 00:00:47.135
But this is the book we found.

00:00:47.135 --> 00:01:07.994
' And Sister Billye Brim, the big prayer warrior, my mama prayer warrior is what I call her—she is an amazing woman of God—she told us about this book this week, and I just wanted to tell you all this book is amazing if you find it.

00:01:08.988 --> 00:01:10.701
It's on Amazon, right?

00:01:10.701 --> 00:01:10.923
Yeah.

00:01:10.923 --> 00:01:14.509
Or you can find it on eBay or probably a lot of other sites.

00:01:14.509 --> 00:01:16.676
Yeah, there's probably a lot of places you can find it.

00:01:16.676 --> 00:01:19.810
You just have to Google it or whatever and you can find this book.

00:01:19.810 --> 00:01:22.600
But I encourage every believer to read it.

00:01:22.600 --> 00:01:25.840
I think you read half of it today, Timmy.

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:29.703
But it gets you so excited about heaven.

00:01:29.703 --> 00:01:33.120
It gets you so excited about what's coming.

00:01:33.120 --> 00:01:35.230
Folks, the future's bright.

00:01:35.230 --> 00:01:39.624
I just told Diana, I said, 'I have to take a break.

00:01:39.624 --> 00:01:47.273
You have to read it slower because I want to download and just process what this man is saying about what he saw.

00:01:47.273 --> 00:02:02.176
' He had an accident—not to be a spoiler alert, but he had an accident—and he died for eight hours and he came back, and the testimony of what the Lord showed him when he was there is breathtaking.

00:02:02.176 --> 00:02:04.799
It's just absolutely wow.

00:02:04.799 --> 00:02:07.075
So, I encourage you to read this book.

00:02:07.075 --> 00:02:12.019
I don't know him, but she recommended it and I trust her immensely.

00:02:12.019 --> 00:02:13.199
So, all right.

00:02:13.519 --> 00:02:18.731
But let me tell you now what I saw the last time we prayed together.

00:02:18.731 --> 00:02:23.940
He showed me an alarm clock with hands straight up.

00:02:23.940 --> 00:02:39.072
I saw the alarm clock going off, and there was a man in the bed asleep, and he was not hearing the alarm clock that was so loud going off above him.

00:02:39.344 --> 00:02:44.622
It was on a shelf, and I could see the room was white and it had books on the shelf.

00:02:44.622 --> 00:02:46.880
It was a bedroom and I could see the person.

00:02:46.880 --> 00:02:59.440
He was asleep and the alarm clock was going off, but because he did not wake up, the Lord said, 'Now there's going to be a great shaking to awaken.

00:02:59.440 --> 00:03:07.430
' And I saw the Lord taking the body of this man and moving him like this to wake him up.

00:03:07.430 --> 00:03:14.239
And He said, 'What's about to take place will wake up the remnant.

00:03:14.239 --> 00:03:20.400
Most of the people—what's about to take place will wake up everyone.

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:28.480
I don't know how you're going to sleep through what's coming, but maybe some will, but most will wake up.

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:34.053
' And so then the Lord said to me, 'You want the greater glory.

00:03:34.053 --> 00:03:39.676
You want the greater outpouring, and this is what it's going to take to get it.

00:03:39.676 --> 00:03:44.960
' And I saw each person, each individual person, we were all different colors.

00:03:44.960 --> 00:03:54.011
We all had different garments on, but each one of us was playing an instrument in an orchestra.

00:03:54.011 --> 00:04:02.296
Some were the brass with the tubas and the horns and all the trumpets and all the beautiful sound.

00:04:02.296 --> 00:04:04.479
Some of them were the drums.

00:04:04.479 --> 00:04:06.200
Some of them were the cymbals.

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:12.205
Some were the chimes, some of them were the harps—all the beautiful things, right?

00:04:12.205 --> 00:04:20.364
But as we played together as one body, we made beautiful music together.

00:04:20.364 --> 00:04:29.360
And then I saw a puzzle, and each person was a puzzle piece to what God wanted to do to join His bride and His people together.

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:35.920
But He said to me, 'So many of My people in the body have gone and started to be lone rangers.

00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:40.271
They don't want to be a body anymore because they're offended.

00:04:40.271 --> 00:04:44.533
' So they say, 'Well, I serve the Lord by myself.

00:04:44.533 --> 00:04:49.226
I don't have to have a relationship with the church because they've hurt me.

00:04:49.226 --> 00:04:51.160
I don't want to be a part of the church.

00:04:51.160 --> 00:04:52.650
' And they had an attitude about the church.

00:04:52.650 --> 00:04:54.467
So they just said, 'Well, I'm a Christian.

00:04:54.467 --> 00:04:55.680
I fellowship by myself.

00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:59.120
' And they just wanted to be alone like a lone ranger.

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:03.799
And He said, 'There are no more lone rangers in the body of Christ.

00:05:03.799 --> 00:05:08.847
You must come together as the days approach.

00:05:08.847 --> 00:05:19.299
Forsake not the assembling of yourselves together, and even more so as the days get closer and closer.

00:05:19.299 --> 00:05:21.177
' Basically, what the Word says.

00:05:21.177 --> 00:05:24.587
He said, 'Brandon, I'm calling My body back together.

00:05:24.587 --> 00:05:41.874
' And He said, 'If you don't get along with that fold, then repent and go find one that you can, and be led by the Spirit of the Lord and find a body that you can go to and be a part of that congregation that you feel comfortable being with.

00:05:41.874 --> 00:05:44.196
But don't make the excuse, 'I'm a lone ranger.

00:05:44.196 --> 00:05:45.600
I serve the Lord by myself.

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:50.560
' Okay, that's what He was saying to me in this vision.

00:05:50.560 --> 00:05:55.004
And He said, 'Each one of My kids is a vital part of the puzzle.

00:05:55.004 --> 00:06:00.773
Each one of My kids—there's not one greater and there's not one smaller.

00:06:00.773 --> 00:06:05.440
Each person provides music and brings their supply.

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:17.783
They bring their supply to prayer, their supply to the church, and each person brings that supply, and it makes us all sound beautiful together.

00:06:17.783 --> 00:06:24.640
' But if you hear some drum off by itself, it's just a drum.

00:06:24.640 --> 00:06:29.640
But a drum that's with a choir with an orchestra sounds beautiful, doesn't it?

00:06:29.640 --> 00:06:31.186
It makes beautiful music.

00:06:31.186 --> 00:06:33.626
You go, 'Wow.

00:06:33.626 --> 00:06:37.600
' It's so important that we function as a body, is what the Lord said.

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:42.983
Without strife, without discord, without all this stuff, we flow together.

00:06:42.983 --> 00:06:46.269
And it was beautiful, the way He painted the whole picture to me.

00:06:46.269 --> 00:06:47.440
I was like, 'Wow.

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:54.960
' And then He talked about Acts chapter 2, verse 1, I believe it is—I don't remember exactly, it was around there.

00:06:54.960 --> 00:07:08.011
He talked about how, before the great mighty wind of the Holy Spirit with cloven tongues as of fire, they were all joined together in one accord, with one voice, with one accord.

00:07:10.720 --> 00:07:15.794
And then a sound from heaven as a mighty rushing wind came.

00:07:15.794 --> 00:07:25.614
But before the great outpouring of the Holy Spirit in Acts chapter 2, they were of one voice and one accord.

00:07:25.614 --> 00:07:28.925
And the Lord said, 'This is what I'm looking for.

00:07:28.925 --> 00:07:38.615
If you want the greater outpouring, you must be one voice and one accord in prayer, functioning as a body.

00:07:38.615 --> 00:07:47.055
Not lone rangers, as a body—one voice, one sound flowing together.

00:07:47.055 --> 00:07:50.113
' And then He talked to me about that.

00:07:50.113 --> 00:07:55.280
He said, 'I'm bringing the finances because I saw a rocket ship.

00:07:55.280 --> 00:07:57.360
' And He said, 'I'm taking you to the outer stratosphere.

00:07:57.360 --> 00:08:00.617
' He used a word that I'm not really familiar with.

00:08:00.617 --> 00:08:08.019
And He told me, He said, 'Brandon, I'm taking this rocket ship, but the rocket fuel is going to be the finances.

00:08:08.019 --> 00:08:17.550
' And He said it will be so much so that He gave me the scripture of Moses and how he told the children of Israel, 'There's too much.

00:08:17.550 --> 00:08:23.839
You can't bring any more of all the blessing because we don't have enough room to receive it all.

00:08:23.839 --> 00:08:48.480
' And the Lord said to me, 'There will be such a surplus and such a blessing on My body, to the remnant of the people who will listen to me on what to do with their finances, that it'll be such a surplus that you'll have more than enough to pay for the churches, for the food, for water, for whatever you've got to do to bring in this end-time harvest because the people are coming in.

00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:51.120
' And there won't be a lack among anybody.

00:08:51.120 --> 00:09:02.200
Remember when it said in Acts—also it said that they sold all their possessions and they brought all the money in, and nobody lacked any good thing?

00:09:02.200 --> 00:09:03.519
Nobody lacked anything.

00:09:03.519 --> 00:09:09.620
There was abundance for everybody because everybody took care of everybody.

00:09:09.620 --> 00:09:11.460
They were a family.

00:09:11.460 --> 00:09:16.560
That's why every time I start these videos, I say, 'Good morning, family.

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:24.290
' Because when we get on the other side and you read this book, you're going to see that we're a family up there.

00:09:24.290 --> 00:09:25.800
We're the family of God.

00:09:25.800 --> 00:09:26.610
We're the family.

00:09:26.610 --> 00:09:27.990
We are a family.

00:09:27.990 --> 00:09:30.279
We're not like, 'Oh, well, you know.

00:09:30.279 --> 00:09:37.359
' He even talks about how there are no locks on any doors because there's no crime, but everybody just visits everybody and talks to everybody.

00:09:39.279 --> 00:09:43.303
You go and visit your friend from down the road, and you're saying, "Hey, how are you doing?

00:09:43.303 --> 00:09:44.366
" at their mansion.

00:09:44.366 --> 00:09:49.400
You go down the road and you see there are kids outside playing in heaven.

00:09:50.120 --> 00:10:00.020
He said it's a glorious family, learning and fellowshipping, and folks, it's wonderful.

00:10:00.020 --> 00:10:04.780
But it's not about everybody being in strife; it's about walking in love.

00:10:04.780 --> 00:10:14.469
And I understand there's a lot of people with a lot of different beliefs because there is a lot of different thinking and because we've all been raised differently.

00:10:26.169 --> 00:10:26.427
I get it.

00:10:26.427 --> 00:10:31.760
But God wants us to come together and be one-minded, of one faith in the days ahead.

00:10:38.526 --> 00:10:38.823
And there'll be one great revival.

00:10:38.823 --> 00:10:41.920
There's going to be one great revival.

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:44.364
And so that's what I had for you today.

00:10:44.364 --> 00:10:49.679
That's basically a rundown of the prayer time we had last time.

00:10:55.830 --> 00:10:59.128
And it was beautiful to me because I saw the Father's heart concerning each one of us, that there's not one greater and there's not one smaller or better or whatever.

00:11:11.609 --> 00:11:12.079
It's just we're all a part of the puzzle, and we are a vital piece.

00:11:20.060 --> 00:11:20.440
You're a vital piece to God's plan.

00:11:20.440 --> 00:11:29.620
Every single one of you is a vital piece to God's plan for the future, what He wants to do on this earth, and what He wants to do in heaven for the thousand-year reign.

00:11:29.620 --> 00:11:32.320
Every single one of us has a vital part.

